<readme>
  <package>i2c</package>
  <synopsis>RoadNarrows Robotics I2C Package</synopsis>
  <description>
The I2C package provides basic interfaces to devices connected
to an I2C Bus.
    <p>
The I2C package provides:
      <ul>
        <li> The libi2c library.</li>
        <li>A set of commmands to interface with an I2C Bus at the byte level.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </description>
  <dependencies>
  RoadNarrows Required Packages:
  <ul>
    <li>rnmake</li>
    <li>librnr</li>
  </ul>
  </dependencies>
  <seealso>See documentation for more details.</seealso>
</readme>
